- Container constant: `apps/adolescent-mental-health/src/lib/site.ts`
- Shared section component: `apps/adolescent-mental-health/src/components/marketing/PageSection.tsx`
- Homepage: `apps/adolescent-mental-health/src/app/page.tsx`

## Virtual IOP page hierarchy (`/virtual-iop-for-teens`)

Flagship program page — bento and editorial modality rows are allowed here.

| Order | Section | Background |
|-------|---------|------------|
| 1 | `ProgramHeroSection` (full-bleed photo + glass stat panel) | dark image |
| 2 | What Is Virtual IOP bento + stat strip | white |
| 3 | Program Structure modality rows | dark |
| 4 | `GoodFitSection` | white |
| 5 | `SessionStructureSection` (intake timeline) | surface |
| 6 | Comparison table | dark |
| 7 | Conditions treated grid | white |
| 8 | `ClinicalMethodsSection` | surface |
| 9 | `TherapyFaqSection` | surface |
| 10 | `DarkCtaSection` | dark |

**CTA rule:** Hero + final `DarkCtaSection` only — no mid-page phone bands in fit, intake, clinical, or FAQ sections.

**Dedup rule:** Anchor `9–20 hrs` in hero badge + stat strip + care ladder; anchor `24–48 hr intake` in hero chips + stat strip + comparison table.
